snippet.textDisplay:
اور راج کرے گی خلق خدا
جو میں بھی ہوں اور تم بھی ہو۔۔۔۔۔۔۔۔

Would never thought any version of this masterpiece but Iqbal Bano sahiba's would taste this good to not only the ears but the soul.... I don't quite know the technicalities of music, but the idea of pluralism, the theme of inclusiveness - From chitral to Balochistan, Muslims & Hindus & Christians, our transgenders, the young & the old - is mesmerizing in itself... And what better phrases than this message of Hope
"ہم دیکھیں گے"

#CokeStudio11 #Pakistan 🇵🇰
